Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:09.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:19.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:06.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:14.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:20.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:27.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:01.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who are you? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,How'd you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:11.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns really\Nare nothing like Similes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I asked who you were.\NAlso, those clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:19.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Waporif!\NShe's one of our new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.\NI didn't know you were a sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:26.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not at all.\NI should be apologizing to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:28.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,The helical motors\Nwere discovered like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:38.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,...two spiral-shaped\Ndevices always in pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:42.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,And so that humans could\Nboard and control them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:46.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,...two cockpits and instrument\Npanels were added later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:50.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,The collective term we\Nuse for convenience is Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Most likely,\Nwhat's controlling this side is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:02:59.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Most likely?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:03.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right. Most likely,\Nwhat's controlling this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:08.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,...first existed in space. Perhaps\Nwe should call it the power of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:13.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,And controlling the other side is what\Nwe might call the power of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:16.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's uncertain too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:17.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:21.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually, we know almost\Nnothing about the helical motors...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:24.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that were excavated\Nfrom the earth's depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:25.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,All we know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:28.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,All we know...\N...is how to operate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:34.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,We only maintain the sections\Nadded on top of the helical motors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:42.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Simile Simouns were built based\Non helical-motor research, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:48.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, but riding them till now, you know\Nthe Similes' capabilities best of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:53.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Compared to Simouns,\NSimiles are just low-quality knockoffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:04:01.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've heard there's no conclusive\Ndata on the Simouns as of yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:03.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not good to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:11.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simouns are holy vessels offered up\Nto Tempus Spatium in sacred rituals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,We regard them accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Exactly, Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:19.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are here to offer\Nthe Ri Majon to Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,As priestesses\Nserving Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm no priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:31.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just want to fly a Simoun.\NI'm not a priestess like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:32.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:41.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm no soldier.\NYou're not either, right, Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, Paraietta. And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:47.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's Morinas, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:49.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's Morinas, Floe.\NOh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:53.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's Morinas, right? Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:58.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Floe.\NJeez, I just can't remember names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:07.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry. When I first saw you, I thought\Nyou were Waporif's new girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,That couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:15.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,My windshield's twisted.\NI want it looked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:22.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the afternoon, I want more details of\Nthe Similes and Simouns' differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:26.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy to.\NNot just with the Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:30.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you ever need to, you can\Nask us anything about this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait. I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:42.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,So was that helpful, Morinas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:45.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'll learn\Nsomething new this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:53.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Distant War
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:45.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am grateful that you've\Nreturned from the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:51.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I assume this means you've chosen\Nto continue on as a Simoun sibylla?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:54.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am still not certain. Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Besides?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am currently without a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:02.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still, you have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're late, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:23.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our ceremony where we gather\Nin the ballroom after breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:27.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, the one from when\Nthe chor was on graveyard shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:33.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, would you like to have\Na maju session in the pool at 3 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:39.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is compulsory?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:40.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:42.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,At 3 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:46.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a good idea. Let's do it.\NSince we're all a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have lost three comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:55.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,And afterwards,\Nthree more left for the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:59.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,And in this emergency,\Nwe've been relieved of night duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,We were the elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:05.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,As priestesses and as sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:07.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll regain our glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:09.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:14.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just joined, so being in\Na maju with an active chor is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:17.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you're saying to do this at 3 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:20.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this\Nabout 3 PM anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's when...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:34.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,3 PM is always Neviril's maju time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am honored to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:45.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:50.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just joined the most\Npowerful chor... Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:57.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see. Please try to get\Nalong with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:05.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, you team up with Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:09.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought I was paired with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:13.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't be so arrogant just\Nbecause you were once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:17.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,First of all, no one thinks\Nyou're capable of replacing Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:25.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're all gathering at\Nthe pool at 3 PM for a maju.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:30.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's when you always have\Na maju, right, Sibylla Aurea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:34.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,If your pair for that isn't\Nset yet, please choose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:42.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, maju pairs are always\Ndetermined by the natural flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not set in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:48.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I would be honored to pair up\Nwith you, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:50.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:27.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. That won't inflict\Nany real damage to the Arcus Prima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:33.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are proud candidates\Nfor the Simoun sibylla post.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold your heads higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:48.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's more than usual,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go out too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:52.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:55.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're off combat duty right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:30.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're showering more\Ngreetings than usual today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:34.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Such long-distance tactics\Nare just harassment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:36.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but the damage isn't zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking\NI'd like to take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is Chor Tempest finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:47.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can make up\Nfor the losses somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:52.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. No matter what the remedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:57.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,...unless she returns,\NChor Tempest will remain scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're early, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,You too, Alty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:19.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's still a half hour till 3 PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you're here, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I stopped by your room to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:35.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you're sisters,\Nwhy don't you fly a Simoun together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:40.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Being sisters has nothing to do with\Nthe chemistry of auriga and sagitta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,You tried?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's clear enough without trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:59.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,When this ship was a private\Ncruiser for observing Ri Majons...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it must've been a sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:07.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now it's been overhauled into\Na battle mother ship for Simoun chors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:11.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,No more gentlemen and\Nladies coming and going...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:14.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even on this beautiful\Nafternoon bathed in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:20.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there's no one gathered before the\Ngigantic central ballroom except us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:21.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:29.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't want it to change like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:41.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,It looks so fun! I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can't I fly this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:46.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simouns can't fly with\None pilot, unlike Similes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:50.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,It needs one more\Nperson aboard, your pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:58.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Helical motors activate when they\Nreceive Tempus Spatium's grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:05.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if either the auriga or sagitta\Nis missing, it can't receive this grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:07.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Both members of\Nthe pair must be aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:10.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:11.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,When did you go\Nto the Spring, Waporif?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Two years and\Nfour months ago, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:24.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,When I met Floe this morning, there\Nwas a strange tension with you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:28.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, actually, Floe and I\Nused to be in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I-In love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:35.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Inappropriate with a Simoun sibylla,\Nthe symbol of utmost respect, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:38.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it is a little awkward now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:55.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're going to the pool, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I told you. I'm not\Ngoing to join in the maju.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won't choose anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:02.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:03.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:10.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened to Amuria was tragic.\NShe was a dear comrade to us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:15.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,After that, I think I understand why\Nsome of us headed for the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:30.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, more... More powerful, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:34.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, don't look! You can't\Nkill them if you see their eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:44.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, Morinas.\NAny pairing is allowed in the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't have to think\Nabout your battle partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:52.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it's first come, first served.\NPair up with whomever you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:18:00.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe Neviril won't\Ncome if we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:05.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,A maju without Neviril\Nwon't be much practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:07.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:13.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess that's too bad, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe Neviril won't come after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:26.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shall I call her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say\Nthings you're not capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:33.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even though she went to\Nthe Spring, Neviril came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:40.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,That means she decided to remain\Na Simoun sibylla of her own will, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:44.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then she will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:37.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NFloe, concentrate harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:38.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:16.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,With these scattered emotions,\Nwe can't achieve a maju.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:20.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even us, Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:23.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:27.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think you're jumping\Nto conclusions a little too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:42.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:02.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:16.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard\Nyou try to protect them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:18.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...this is the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.02,0:22:26.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll... I'll get you out right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:27.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fire unit, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:47.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:52.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.08,0:22:59.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:06.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.57,0:23:19.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:24.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:28.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:32.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:38.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.70,0:23:44.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:47.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:53.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.34,0:23:59.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:06.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.15,0:24:11.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone! Get a move on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:15.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.16,0:24:17.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Nearby War.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:19.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Nearby War
